What you need to know:

Reaching his century of Tottenham goals was a landmark moment for Son, who is the 18th player to score 100 in all competitions for the north London club and the first from outside the United Kingdom and IrelandThe only frustration for Mourinho was a stoppage-time red card for Matt Doherty after the Republic of Ireland right-back received a second bookingHaving ended their disappointing run of four league games without a win, Tottenham moved within four points of leaders Liverpool, who play Southampton on Monday